nodes.text: The Bronze Nimbus was one of several Special forces units in the Jabiimi Military.

Prior to the Clone Wars, Alto Stratus served as a Commander in the unit. When he became disillusioned with the cowardice of the Jabiim Army, he used the Bronze Nimbus as the core for what would become the Nationalist Army. Eventually, Bronze Nimbus was transformed into the Nimbus commandos.
